### 1. Home completo (publico)
GET {{baseUrl}}/home

###

### 2. Somente menu (publico)
GET {{baseUrl}}/home/menu

###

### 3. Atualizar ordem das categorias da home (protegido)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/home/categories
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "categoryIds": [
    "{{categoryId1}}",
    "{{categoryId2}}",
    "{{categoryId3}}"
  ]
}

###

### 4. Forcar refresh do cache diario da home (protegido)
POST {{baseUrl}}/home/refresh
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 5. Validar nova ordem no menu (publico)
GET {{baseUrl}}/home/menu

###
